nodes.title: howto
widgets_values:
NAVIGATION
ALT+C (OPT+C) to open/collapse nodes.
` 1 2 3 4 keys to switch between proofing and over view 
CTRL-B to bypass a node.

STEP BY STEP
1 ⭕Prompt from +T5X3 and - "Convert Input" on G+ or L+ to write individual prompts.
2 ⭕Parameters, set in Selector, Seed, Load ⟷. default_scale gets filename number
3 ⭕Checkpoint file, set 1(any) or 2(XL). Stages share models & focus their own.
4 ⭕LoadVAE, ensure Stage checkpoint matches, or bypass for ckpt with built-in vae.
5 ⭕Save path and filename..
6 ⭕I/O groups disable/enable unused. Run one Stage at a time on old hardware.
7 queue!
NOTES
- Collapse nodes before mute/bypass buttons. Nodes crossing groups causes issues.
- 'Last Queued' empties on browser refresh
- ⭕LoadLatent or LoadLmage take priority over Empty Latent unless bypassed
- In Load⟷, set default as the x# from the file name
- Enable interposer when converting between v1.5/xl/etc. models
- To adjust group positions, raise logo window from bottom right corner
- Each image chimes & notifies browser by default. snake alertsICON KEY
⭕ 	common user-ready settings
⟷ 	upscaler
↭ 	downscaler
+ 	positive conditioning chain
- 	negative conditioning chain
▟	steps
|  	stage 1 process
|| 	stage 2 process
↻ 	failsafe (automated, essential)
⇲ 	clip encoding scale
⌥ 	list output
🐍 	no step on snek (alert!)
m 	Model
V 	VAE
L 	Latent
i 	Image
C 	Cascade
3 	SD3
